---

<section data-animate class="py-20 bg-[#0f172a] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-[#f97316]/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6" style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;">
      Sem risco para si
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mb-4">
      Paga 50% para começar, 50% na entrega. Vê o progresso a cada etapa.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white/80 text-xl font-semibold">
      Só paga o segundo pagamento quando estiver <span class="text-[#f97316]">100% satisfeito</span>.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 mt-10 text-sm text-white/40">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#25d366" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        Sem contratos longos
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#25d366" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        Sem mensalidades
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#25d366" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        30 dias de suporte grátis
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
